1277
01:31:23,861 --> 01:31:26,245
<i>We don't even know its purpose.</i>

1278
01:31:28,782 --> 01:31:31,850
<i>'Cause I would have
stayed among you longer,</i>

1279
01:31:31,918 --> 01:31:34,303
<i>but that wind is taking me away.</i>

1280
01:31:39,710 --> 01:31:41,677
<i>I will miss it here,</i>

1281
01:31:43,063 --> 01:31:45,013
<i>and I will miss you.</i>

1282
01:31:46,800 --> 01:31:50,870
<i>But I'm content that the
power that propels me</i>

1283
01:31:52,039 --> 01:31:55,224
<i>does so with superior knowledge</i>

1284
01:31:56,143 --> 01:31:58,394
<i>as to what is for the best,</i>

1285
01:32:00,730 --> 01:32:02,698
<i>and that is my faith.</i>

1286
01:32:07,053 --> 01:32:09,822
<i>I would like to come
