01:34:16,999 --> 01:34:18,434
Thank you, Sister.

1307
01:34:18,501 --> 01:34:21,737
You were missed.
How is your brother?

1308
01:34:21,805 --> 01:34:23,572
Better. Much better.

1309
01:34:23,640 --> 01:34:26,676
I'm very glad.
I prayed for him.

1310
