It was good to get away.
I needed to see my family.

1311
01:34:31,231 --> 01:34:34,683
Mmm. Then I'm glad
you did it.

1312
01:34:38,120 --> 01:34:40,222
And Father Flynn is gone?

1313
01:34:41,524 --> 01:34:42,691
Yes.

1314
01:34:45,695 --> 01:34:48,129
So you did it.
You got him out.

1315
01:34:48,815 --> 01:34:49,882
Yes.

