Saint Jerome Church and School.

1335
01:36:11,982 --> 01:36:13,632
It's a promotion.

1336
01:36:15,118 --> 01:36:16,801
You didn't tell them?

1337
01:36:16,869 --> 01:36:21,640
Oh, I told our good monsignor.
I crossed the garden, and I told him.

1338
01:36:25,145 --> 01:36:27,713
He did not believe it
to be true.

1339
01:36:31,551 --> 01:36:34,269
Then why did Father Flynn go?

