That I had called a nun
in his previous parish,

1342
01:36:42,562 --> 01:36:46,915
that I had found out his prior
history of infringements.

1343
01:36:52,155 --> 01:36:53,989
So you did prove it?

1344
01:36:58,544 --> 01:37:00,346
I made no such call.

1345
01:37:04,534 --> 01:37:05,835
You lied?

1346
01:37:06,719 --> 01:37:08,620
Yes.

1347
01:37:08,688 --> 01:37:13,458
But if he'd had no such history,
the lie wouldn't have worked.

1348
01:37:16,979 --> 01:37:19,615
His resignation
was his confession.

1349
01:37:24,604 --> 01:37:27,073
He was what I thought he was.

1350
01:37:30,009 --> 01:37:31,744
And he's gone.

1351
01:37:36,499 --> 01:37:38,600
I can't believe you lied.

1352
01:37:44,357 --> 01:37:46,709
In the pursuit of wrongdoing,

1353
01:37:47,677 --> 01:37:50,196
one steps away from God.

1354
01:37:53,884 --> 01:37:56,134
Of course, there is a price.

1355
01:38:04,644 --> 01:38:05,844
I see.

1356
01:38:14,788 --> 01:38:15,854
Oh.

1357
